&lt;h2&gt;The Implementation:&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Just a note: I'm using &lt;a href=&quot;http://jashkenas.github.com/coffee-script/&quot;&gt;CoffeeScript&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://ender.no.de/#jeesh&quot;&gt;The Jeesh&lt;/a&gt; (though you can use mootools/jQuery/prototype as you please) and &lt;a href=&quot;http://sass-lang.com/&quot;&gt;Sass&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is the demo of the functionality: &lt;abbr title=&quot;Cascading Style Sheets&quot;&gt;CSS&lt;/abbr&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And below is source code:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;!--- TODO: figure out a way to fix the 'missing coffee lexer' bug --&gt;


&lt;p&gt;``` coffeescript&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;$.domReady -&amp;gt;
  $('abbr[title]').each -&amp;gt;
    title = this.getAttribute 'title'
    this.setAttribute 'data-title', title
    this.removeAttribute 'title'
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;```&lt;/p&gt;

